CatDescriptText: St. Paul Baptist church occupied this modern brick building with double staircase before moving to their present location on Penn Avenue at Washington Boulevard.  This church building is now the King of Kings Baptist Church.
TitMainTitle: St. Paul Baptist Church, 5169 Broad Street, Garfield
